475
00:26:12,430 --> 00:26:14,260
Air di danau ini jernih.

476
00:26:14,390 --> 00:26:14,820
Ini...

477
00:26:15,190 --> 00:26:16,340
Apa yang ingin kau katakan?

478
00:26:17,230 --> 00:26:18,230
Aku ingin...

479
00:26:19,950 --> 00:26:21,470
- Kau tidak bilang, aku pergi.
