480
00:26:21,870 --> 00:26:22,260
Tunggu dulu.

481
00:26:23,820 --> 00:26:25,100
Kau letakkan barangmu dulu.

482
00:26:32,500 --> 00:26:32,910
Pegang ini.

483
00:26:37,430 --> 00:26:38,100
Apa ini?

484
00:26:39,670 --> 00:26:41,230
Ini pengeras suara.

485
00:26:42,100 --> 00:26:43,260
Pengeras suara?

486
00:26:43,710 --> 00:26:44,990
Coba letakkan di telingamu.

487
00:26:51,500 --> 00:26:52,260
Aku...

488
00:26:53,500 --> 00:26:56,340
Aku ingin mengundangmu ke pesta akademi.

489
00:26:57,710 --> 00:26:58,260
Aku tahu

490
00:26:59,340 --> 00:27:02,190
meskipun cara ini agak aneh, aku...

491
00:27:03,340 --> 00:27:03,780
Aku mau.

492
00:27:11,020 --> 00:27:11,500
Terima kasih.

493
00:27:14,910 --> 00:27:15,260
Apa?

494
00:27:17,430 --> 00:27:19,540
Kubilang terima kasih.

495
00:27:21,340 --> 00:27:22,580
Aku tidak kedengaran.

496
00:27:23,390 --> 00:27:25,950
Terima kasih, Fang.

497
00:27:27,540 --> 00:27:28,060
Baiklah.

498
00:27:28,340 --> 00:27:30,230
Kalau begitu, aku akan
dengan enggan menerimanya.

499
00:27:32,710 --> 00:27:36,990
Kalau begitu, suamiku,
kita akan menari di mana?

500
00:27:40,190 --> 00:27:45,430
Kita akan menari tarian sederhana
dan menyenangkan di akademi.

501
00:27:46,540 --> 00:27:49,020
Menari tarian sederhana, ya?

502
00:27:56,390 --> 00:27:58,390
Aku masih harus menulis buku cerita,
aku pergi dulu.

503
00:28:10,910 --> 00:28:12,910
Maukah kau menemaniku ke pesta?

504
00:28:15,260 --> 00:28:15,870
Aku mau.

505
00:28:19,470 --> 00:28:21,230
Mengapa Pangeran tidak terlihat
akhir-akhir ini?

506
00:28:22,100 --> 00:28:24,230
Pangeran ada urusan penting,
keluar kediaman beberapa hari.

507
00:28:25,670 --> 00:28:26,500
Urusan penting?

508
00:28:27,100 --> 00:28:27,990
Dia kesulitan bergerak.

509
00:28:28,260 --> 00:28:30,990
Jika ada urusan penting,
mengapa dia tidak membawamu?

510
00:28:31,100 --> 00:28:32,780
Mungkinkah dia bersembunyi
dari Putri kita?

511
00:28:33,100 --> 00:28:35,340
Tidak mungkin,
Pangeran sangat menyukai Putri,

512
00:28:35,390 --> 00:28:36,390
mana mungkin sembunyi darinya?

513
00:28:38,020 --> 00:28:40,100
Mungkin karena metode
pengobatan Putri terlalu...

514
00:28:40,950 --> 00:28:41,430
Terlalu apa?

515
00:28:45,190 --> 00:28:45,740
Begitulah.

516
00:28:47,710 --> 00:28:48,020
Begini.

517
00:29:06,630 --> 00:29:07,190
Aku mengerti.

518
00:29:07,540 --> 00:29:08,470
Aku tahu dua jurus ini.

519
00:29:09,340 --> 00:29:12,100
Jurus pertama, tangkap tangan, pertama,
kait pergelangan tangan, lalu putar.

520
00:29:12,870 --> 00:29:15,020
Jurus kedua,
cekik leher, aku bisa keduanya.

521
00:29:16,540 --> 00:29:17,300
Bukan.

522
00:29:17,710 --> 00:29:18,190
Mari.

523
00:29:18,340 --> 00:29:18,820
Tarik aku.

524
00:29:18,950 --> 00:29:19,820
Tarik aku.

525
00:29:20,780 --> 00:29:21,740
Tarik aku.

526
00:29:22,340 --> 00:29:22,870
Tarik ke arahmu.

527
00:29:23,260 --> 00:29:23,500
Kuat.

528
00:29:26,470 --> 00:29:26,740
Benar.

529
00:29:27,230 --> 00:29:28,430
Lalu, putar.

530
00:29:47,340 --> 00:29:48,470
Aku belum pernah melihat jurus ini.

531
00:29:51,060 --> 00:29:51,740
Minggir.

532
00:29:53,260 --> 00:29:54,540
Kenapa kau menyentuhku?

533
00:29:55,390 --> 00:29:56,780
Aku tidak menyentuhmu.

534
00:29:57,950 --> 00:29:58,580
Kau masih bilang.

535
00:29:59,150 --> 00:30:01,820
Jika ini tersebar,
aku tidak akan bisa menikah.

536
00:30:01,950 --> 00:30:03,230
Aku akan menjadi hantu gentayangan.

537
00:30:03,540 --> 00:30:05,740
Siapa bilang kau tidak bisa menikah?

538
00:30:14,020 --> 00:30:14,820
Kau menyebalkan.

539
00:30:14,820 --> 00:30:15,470
Apa katamu?

540
00:30:18,470 --> 00:30:21,340
(Ada apa? Dia gila, ya?)

541
00:30:26,540 --> 00:30:27,630
Kemari.

542
00:30:30,150 --> 00:30:31,230
Terima kasih.

543
00:30:33,740 --> 00:30:35,740
Kenapa Fang masih belum datang?

544
00:30:37,230 --> 00:30:38,500
Ini gadis yang kubilang hari itu.

545
00:30:38,740 --> 00:30:39,500
Dia?

546
00:30:39,910 --> 00:30:41,230
Kau pilih siapa
untuk menari bersama nanti?

547
00:30:42,060 --> 00:30:42,820
Orang itu belum datang.

548
00:30:44,500 --> 00:30:45,260
Apa yang Guru Ji lakukan?

549
00:30:48,100 --> 00:30:50,580
Bagaimana Guru Ji bisa
membuat Nyonya Guru senang?

550
00:30:54,910 --> 00:30:55,710
Ambil ini.

551
00:30:59,190 --> 00:30:59,740
Baik.

552
00:31:02,150 --> 00:31:04,630
Apa maksudmu?

553
00:31:05,430 --> 00:31:08,430
Guru Ji, nanti saat Nyonya Guru muncul,

554
00:31:08,870 --> 00:31:11,580
berikan bunga ini padanya,
dia pasti akan senang.

555
00:31:12,100 --> 00:31:14,820
Apakah ini bisa berhasil?

556
00:31:15,100 --> 00:31:15,990
Tentu saja.

557
00:31:16,430 --> 00:31:18,020
Aku sudah berkecimpung
di dunia asmara bertahun-tahun

558
00:31:18,100 --> 00:31:19,100
dan tidak pernah gagal.

559
00:31:22,990 --> 00:31:23,740
Guru Ji,

560
00:31:24,910 --> 00:31:26,630
jika kau berani mengecewakan Nyonya Guru,

561
00:31:27,630 --> 00:31:28,780
nanti jika aku bertemu denganmu,

562
00:31:29,340 --> 00:31:32,430
aku akan memanggil sekelompok wanita
untuk menerkammu.

563
00:31:40,340 --> 00:31:42,670
Selanjutnya adalah waktu tarian bebas.

564
00:31:59,630 --> 00:32:00,670
Guru Ji, cepatlah.

565
00:32:02,430 --> 00:32:02,820
Cepat.

566
00:32:19,060 --> 00:32:20,260
Bunga yang sangat indah.

567
00:32:22,990 --> 00:32:23,710
Aku...

568
00:32:24,950 --> 00:32:26,710
Bisakah kita berdansa?

569
00:32:26,710 --> 00:32:27,230
Tentu saja.

570
00:33:32,597 --> 00:33:36,957
♪Awan di ujung langit
terbentang tidak bertepi♪

571
00:33:39,797 --> 00:33:44,197
♪Dari ketinggian kupandangi mata
yang rindu menatap jauh♪

572
00:33:45,757 --> 00:33:48,927
♪Waktu masih terus berjalan♪

573
00:33:49,547 --> 00:33:52,107
♪Menyisakan jejak siapa di bumi ini?♪

574
00:33:52,507 --> 00:33:58,967
♪Bukan sekadar berani
karena hati terikat pada cinta ini♪

575
00:34:00,597 --> 00:34:03,407
♪Kita ditakdirkan tidak bisa mendekat♪

576
00:34:04,247 --> 00:34:07,327
♪Anggap saja cinta
